title: 14.385 EFFECT OF NONPUBLICATION OF EXEMPT RULES.
text:
No rule, as defined in section 14.02, subdivision 4, which is exempt from the rulemaking provisions of this chapter has the force and effect of law as of January 1, 1985, unless prior to that date it has been submitted to the revisor for publication in Minnesota Rules.
The revisor has the same editorial powers over these rules as the revisor has over nonexempt rules.
